+    """Let ATOM-owned MiniMax-M3 handle checkpoint MXFP8 metadata itself.
+
+    vLLM's online MXFP8 shorthand is valid for CLI usage, but vLLM currently
+    refuses to build that quant config from a checkpoint-side
